	<string id="st_wpn_vepr134_descr">
		<text> The Vepr (Ukrainian: "Wild Boar") is a semi-auto civilian hunting rifle based on RPK light machine gun and produced by Molot factory from Russia. Veprs found their way to The Zone as Stalkers often took their hunting rifles there, instead of buying military weapons on black market. They are well liked and sometimes preferred over AKs due to their higher accuracy and range.\n
		This variant is chambered in 7.62x39mm.\n
		%c[ui_gray_2]ATTACHMENTS:\n 
		%c[d_purple] • %c[ui_gray_2] Scopes for Picatinny rail</text>
	</string>

